1. rails new myApp --api (Refer to the active_model_serializers_rails_5_api app)

2. follow this guide.  http://sourcey.com/building-the-prefect-rails-5-api-only-app/

3. add active_model_serializers gem and configure it. refer to rails_json.txt file in documents.

4. in postman in postman add - 
 
   header: Content-Type, value: application/json

   (if using authorization from the guide above use below line. copy token value from the user record.)
   header: Authorization, value: Token token=A78qr4NE9ixjXdbR8UMsBQtt

               
